Package: netavark
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, aardvark-dns, nftables
Description: Container network stack
 Netavark is a container network stack written in Rust. It is
 designed to work with Podman but can be used with other OCI
 container management applications. It provides bridge networking,
 port forwarding, firewall rules, and DNS integration via
 aardvark-dns.
